# Signal Branding for AI Features

All AI-powered features in the portal must use **Signal branding**, not generic "AI" language.

## Naming

- Use **"Signal Recommendations"** not "AI Recommendations"
- Use **"Signal Insights"** not "AI Insights"
- Use **"Powered by Signal"** not "Powered by AI"
- Use **"Signal"** as the product name for any AI-driven feature

## Icon

Always use the custom `SignalIcon` component instead of generic icons like `Brain`, `Sparkles`, or `Bot` when labeling AI features:

```jsx
import SignalIcon from '@/components/ui/SignalIcon'

// ✅ GOOD
<SignalIcon className="h-5 w-5" />
<span>Signal Recommendations</span>

// ❌ BAD
<Brain className="h-5 w-5" />
<span>AI Recommendations</span>
```

The `SignalIcon` component lives at `@/components/ui/SignalIcon` and accepts `className`, `size`, and `color` props. It uses `currentColor` like lucide icons.
